ucture where the critical and the sonic points will be identical.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jun 2018 16:09:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 8 Dec 2018 12:32:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-11"}
