 filtered $J$-band detector, with small color corrections. In the course of\nour sky testing, we successfully measured sub-percent flux variations in an\nexoplanet transit. We have demonstrated an ability to detect transient sources\nin dense fields using image subtraction of existing reference catalogs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jun 2018 20:12:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-16"}
